modules.description: Generates XML sitemaps by constructing and serializing entries with URLs, last modification dates, and change frequencies. It works with custom record types representing sitemap entries and a collection of these entries. Used to automate the creation of sitemap files for website indexing by search engines.

Generates XML sitemaps by validating and formatting URLs with priority, change frequency, and last modification date. It processes URLs with specific constraints, such as protocol inclusion and character limits, and outputs structured XML content. Functions include converting change frequencies to strings, validating URLs, and writing sitemap data to buffers or XML streams.
